casebody.data:
November 7, 1949.

Per Curiam Decisions.

No. 342. Vinsonhaler et al., doing business as KGHI Broadcasting Service, et al. v. Beard, Collector. Bruce T. Bullion and Eugene R. Warren for appellants. T. J. Gentry for appellee. Per Curiam:

The appeal is dismissed for want of a substantial federal question. Crutcher v. Kentucky, 141 U. S. 47.

Mr. Justice Douglas took no part in the consideration or decision of this case.
